$interpreted: Slums Older Brother: Cin, your sacrifice saved us all...
Slums Younger Brother: We will never forget you...
Slums Male: May Hyacinthus rest in peace.
Elder: ...*sigh*...so many have fallen, why has this happened to us...
Lio: Cin, we're here to say goodbye......
Nigel: You're here too?
Angelia: Yeah...
Nigel: ...For helping drive away the monsters, thank you both for that.
Naya: It was nothing... if you need our help, just let us know.
Angelia: You must have a lot to tell Hyacinthus. We won't disturb you.
Angelia: Naya, let's go.
Nigel: Are you sure these reports are true!?
Slums Male: Yes, leader.
Slums Female: We've investigated the matter very carefully, that's Angel's true identity...
Nigel: ...I understand, that'll be it for now.
Yamitsuki: Seems like your intelligence organization has finally gotten some worthy news.
Nigel: Eve...Or should I say Yamitsuki?
Yamitsuki: I just paid my respects to Cin's grave...
Nigel: Oh? She uttered your name in her last dying breath. She would have been very happy to see you.
Yamitsuki: ………
Nigel: Don't need to stay by that strange professor's side?
Yamitsuki: I'm here to assist you with your plan.
Nigel: ………
Nigel: Didn't you and Cin disapprove of my actions? What changed your mind?
Yamitsuki: I've got important information. There's someone on the inside who is willing to help.
